    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ArrayIterator, BooleanArrayIterator, ByteArrayIterator, CharacterArrayIterator, CountDownIterator, CountUpIterator, DoubleArrayIterator, EmptyIterator, FloatArrayIterator, IntegerArrayIterator, LongArrayIterator, NodeListIterator, ObjectIterator, OptionalIterator, PairIterator, ShortArrayIterator, TripleIterator, TupleIterator

    public abstract class AbstractIndexedIterator<Payload>
extends AbstractProtectedBidirectionalIterator<Payload>
    An AbstractIndexedIterator is an abstract base implementation for ProtectedBidirectionalIterator implementations that holds the current index and implements the index-related methods.
    Since:
    3.1.1
    Author:
    Torsten Krause (tk at markenwerk dot net)
